1. wirless adapter: NRF24L01
2. servo for control flow of the water: SG-90 
3. servo balance(Controlled by PWM)SG-5010 or MG-995 
4. microcontroller: STM32(Check "Getting started with Stm32 Hardware developer" to get a schematic drawing)
5. bldc for making water to flow:(Controlled by PWM) https://botland.com.pl/silniki-bldc-bezszczotkowe/5188-silnik-bezszczotkowy-z-przekladnia-25dx43l-45-1-ze-sterownikiem-pwm-enkoder-5904422306052.html?cd=18298825651&ad=&kd=&gclid=CjwKCAjw-rOaBhA9EiwAUkLV4geQaOKKD-l3gYV5RXAct9NCja5nMiYdrZ1AbeNjEGxQzgFgSdMZxhoCbZYQAvD_BwE
6. accelerometer (We should make a schematic): ADXL345
7 Connectors(for RC transmission) 
8. Power supply: (18V ->BLDC 6V->Servo 3.3V->STM32) 
